transforms.code:
columns = value['columns']
	data = value['data']
	datasetHeaders = []
	datasetRows = []

	datasetHeaders.append("Congregation")
	for h in range(0,15):
		date = self.getChild("root").getChild("DateSelection").getChild("DateSelectors").props.instances[h].Date
		formatedDate = system.date.format(date,'E MM/d')
		datasetHeaders.append(formatedDate)

	for i in range(data.getRowCount()):
		oneRow = []
		for j in range(data.getColumnCount()):
			if data.getColumnName(j) != 'locationId':
				oneRow.append(data.getValueAt(i,j))
		datasetRows.append(oneRow)
	returnDataSet = system.dataset.toDataSet(datasetHeaders, datasetRows)
	return returnDataSet

import traceback
	try:
